James and Hope Ben Canaan and their 12 children left the Gloriavale Christian Community last month . 
  The Ben Canaan family are adapting well to life outside the New Zealand commune . 
  The father has accepted a farm job and the family have moved to Timaru . 
  Gloriavale is a Christian community of 500 people who reject the outside world . 
  The community was founded by Australian evangelist Neville Cooper . 
  The family left the commune on New Zealand's West Coast . 
 